66ae725ae0b84ddd.name: Bhumir Tathya-বাংলার জমির তথ্য
66ae725ae0b84ddd.dis: # Banglarbhumi Land Record Details - Details of Jomir Tothya (Land Records) - Market Value Information: Market value of land, Market value of flats and apartments - Land Registration Details: Search by owner name, Search by property details, Search for the nearest registration office through Mouza details - West Bengal Government Schemes Related to Land Records - How to Use the Banglarbhumi App? 1. Select the district (জেলা নির্বাচন করুন)। 2. Select the block (ব্লক নির্বাচন করুন)। 3. Select Mouza (মৌজা নির্বাচন করুন)। 4. Two options are available for searching the land records: Plot and Khatiyan. 5. Fill the captcha code. 6. Click on View. 7. To save the file, click on the save icon button.
